{"content": "<h2>The Artist: Ayla El Moussa</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Ayla El Moussa is a crypto artist, illustrator, painter and glitch experimentor,  celebrated for her ethereal and evocative imagery.</p><p>The viewer is often kept at a manageable distance, in a symbolic way that one might feel attempting to get under the skin of a Cy Twombly work. The curves of the female form in 'Mirror Mirror' are obvious yet any connection with the turned away central subject remain elusive. Her fixation is instead with the undulating waves; a continuing thematic across collections.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"649\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-1024x887.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-1024x887.jpg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-300x260.jpg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-768x666.jpg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-1536x1331.jpg 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-2048x1775.jpg 2048w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-1320x1144.jpg 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Mirror-Mirror-Ayla-el-Moussa-600x520.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Mirror Mirror by Ayla el Moussa collected by MintFace</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t'When I no longer see myself in the art, I know it's done.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Ayla el Moussa</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: \"Nude Pixels\"</h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h6>August 2021</h6>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Nude Pixels entered the NFT arena as a 'pinup girl at a distance' during the height of the 2021 NFT boom. The 42 posed forms are superimposed and centered on a neutral skin toned background, again keeping the viewer at arms length.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"748\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-1024x1022.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-1024x1022.png 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-300x300.png 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-150x150.png 150w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-768x767.png 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-400x400.png 400w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-600x599.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa-100x100.png 100w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/nude-pixels-Ayla-el-Moussa.png 1226w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"The closer you look, the less you see.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Ayla el Moussa</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: \"Scene 1\"</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Evoking the carved marble statues from Medici times, 'Scene 1' from The Painted Muse collection is a hand painted study in light and form. The viewer must again wrestle with the occlusion of the entire form through the zoomed in framing. The cloistering of the sodden fabric on the skin is also felt by the viewer.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"791\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-970x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-970x1024.jpg 970w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-284x300.jpg 284w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-768x810.jpg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-1456x1536.jpg 1456w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-1941x2048.jpg 1941w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-1320x1393.jpg 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/Scene-1-The-Painted-Muse-Ayla-el-Moussa-600x633.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Scene 1 by Ayla el Moussa collected by Eniosta</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t<p>Through the lens, the pixels and the paintbrush we get a glimpse of 'Her' and the mystery unfolding. Can we be trusted to fill the entire picture ourselves or does each vignette reveal a depth unattainable to most? Either way, a celebration of the feminine is the overflowing cup of divinity that Ayla's work continually draws from.  </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/ayla-el-moussa/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAyla el Moussa | Line 187\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}